#. 5 holes
  - Camera port : trans umbilcus(12mm)
  - Acting ports : 4 holes(5mm : RUQ, LUQ, 12mm : RLQ, LLQ)  U shape
#. Peritoneal exploration : adhesiolysis
  - A/A/S/S (-/-/-/-)
  - Solid organ abnormality : negative
#. Liver elevation
#. Omentectomy
#. Stomach mobilization and LN dissection
  - LN #4sb, 4d
  - Lt. GEA,V ligation
  - GC clearing
  - LN #6
  - Rt. GEA,V ligation
  - LN #5
  - RGA ligation
  - duodenal mobilization
#. duodenal division with endo GIA 60 purple x1
#. LN #8, 9, 11p
#. LGA, coronary vein ligation and divided, LN#7
#. LC clearing up to cardioesophageal junction, LN#1, 3
#. Stomach division with endo GIA 60 purple x2
#. Transverse minilaparotomy at umbilicus
#. Specimen out
#. BI Delta
  - entry holes made at duodenum and stomach
  - endo GIA 45 purple x1  insertion via each entry hole and fired
  - common hole closure with endo GIA60 purple x1 and GIA45 purple x1
#. Irrigation and meticulous hemostasis
#. JP drain insertion x1
  - Rt ~ under GB ~ behind GD anastomosis ~ spleen
#. Guardix applied
#. Wound closure : layer by layer
#. skin stapler applied
#. Aseptic dressing
', '초기적재');
